{"tid":868668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國研究：2040年中國人比美國人長命","createTime":"2018-10-19T16:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T18:27:37.000Z","uid":13468,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf61b802814ff9318a6dd0a6a9558a98cf63cb4","tid":868668,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181018/s00004/4cf0e829c3a34847e6d835dd571a77be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181018%2Fs00004%2F4cf0e829c3a34847e6d835dd571a77be.jpg&h=29ea65ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國一項研究表示，至2040年，中國人的預期壽命將達81.9歲，美國人則只得79.8歲，是發達國家中排名下滑幅度最大。同時，西班牙可能超越日本，位居預期壽命榜首，達到85.8歲。<br />\n<br />\n該項美國衛生統計評估研究所的研究成果，發表在英國醫學期刊《刺針》，顯示到2040年，全球195個國家中，有59個的人均預期壽命可達到80歲，當中包括中國的81.9歲，當中男性78.6歲，女性84.2歲。中國在2016年人均預期壽命排名第64位，預測到2040年將大升29位，排在全球第39位。<br />\n<br />\n研究指，全球人口在2016至2040年這四分一個世紀，平均壽命可望增長4.4歲，當中包括中國在內的大部分東亞和南亞國家，都有望實現壽命增長5至6歲。<br />\n<br />\n但是，美國人的平均預期壽命在此期間僅增長1.1歲，遠遠低於全球增幅，是所有發達國家之中，排名下降幅度最大的，會從2016年的第43名，下降到2040年的64名，平均預期壽命79.8歲。研究指，美國人的預期壽命，在過去兩年都在下降，重要因素是毒品。此外，美國成人肥胖率達到歷史最高水平，每10名成年人就有4名肥胖，18.5%的青少年也被肥胖困擾。<br />\n<br />\n此外，西班牙預期人均壽命將達到85.8歲，以0.1歲的些微優勢，超過日本的85.7歲。研究指，以蔬果和海鮮為主的地中海飲食將發揮重要作用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00004/1539874898074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00004%2F1539874898074&d=k1mwhY0xzbygSZy31giZGFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e3608ba4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00004%2F1539874898074&h=b4902824\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00004/1539874898074</a>"},{"pid":"6938656966cb0e8ed20ff236265bfa0f4c0159c9","tid":868668,"uid":170044,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"係咪因為2047年香港俾正式列入為中國縣，當中國人對待？"},{"pid":"752c9d9f9a48cea016e12f65eef032eb63bb353b","tid":868668,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6938656966cb0e8ed20ff236265bfa0f4c0159c9","tid":868668,"uid":170044,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"係咪因為2047年香港俾正式列入為中國縣，當中國人對待？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:19:11.000Z","msg":"美國果班中国人叫咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美籍後代"},{"pid":"9c8397ed2dd321bd28abd48494e0484eb04c27b6","tid":868668,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:21:27.000Z","msg":"美國仔濫藥吸毒 好多英年早逝"},{"pid":"ebcef9e59a476b4bebea9494a1fb7674e0fcda47","tid":868668,"uid":193026,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:25:14.000Z","msg":"唔出奇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/inline-images/getaroundroundround_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zerohedge.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Finline-images%2Fgetaroundroundround_0.jpg&h=d197e499&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a98c5bd4b760cbc3f66819a4ea3a65a2b7352b30","tid":868668,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181018/s00004/1539874898074\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181018%2Fs00004%2F1539874898074&h=7a1348d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吸毒 害人害己"},{"pid":"db9a5561b4c0e6c87d6bf6c7004a228fbf9f920e","tid":868668,"uid":17765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"正常人類好難夠啲食盡元素表都唔死嘅畜生鬥喎"},{"pid":"8125568b56948eebf36ca50bad02fd61cbe67787","tid":868668,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"物種進化<br />\n食得太多毒 身體都識進化應對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044a5da73c82eac52f75a4b0738139aa9f0e1815","tid":868668,"uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"這「幾乎是一種形式的戰爭」，毒品「正在殺死我們的人民」，美國總統川普（特朗普）在8月16日的內閣會議上這樣形容來自中國的、以芬太尼為主的類鴉片毒品，「我對此非常堅定。這是一個恥辱，我們可以阻止它」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這並非是美國首次將中共對美的毒品輸出視為一種形式的戰爭，美國軍方在2014年發布的一份白皮書中披露，中共向外輸出「毒品戰」、「文化戰」等非常規戰的可怕目的。那就是，用來破壞對手的道德結構，削弱對手。而無論是「毒品戰」還是「文化戰」實則都屬於中共戰爭論著中提到的「超限戰」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467a192348fdacdaed0875c1a560fe7f282a3b4c","tid":868668,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T16:43:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等睇共慘黨養唔起支那老狗<br />\n起廢老集中營<br />\n呃鳩佢地入去沖涼<br />\n跟手放毒氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"0d44d2c1214ce70c21333346a7995bd89d867758","tid":868668,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"到時社保退休金爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260c1ff72cee8564d57fe9d4d9c1e056932f7814","tid":868668,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d44d2c1214ce70c21333346a7995bd89d867758","tid":868668,"uid":27240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"到時社保退休金爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T18:14:54.000Z","msg":"傻的 支那人比人慢性毒死都唔知咩事啦"},{"pid":"73848976ef83c3102293e9ba2461fc50f6631b18","tid":868668,"uid":52614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB